[SHORT DESC]
Doubles in power with each hit. Repeats for 5 turns.

[LONG DESC]
<p>Doubles in power with each consecutive hit. Locks the user into it for 5 turns. If the user selects Ice Ball after this 5th turn, the base power resets. Using Defense Curl before Ice Ball doubles its base power for as long as the user stays in the battle.
</p>
<h2>Related Moves</h2>
<p><a href="/rs/moves/rollout">Rollout</a> is a Rock-type equivalent.</p>